    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted despite Test conditions factor achieving level 2 against a required level of 3. The single-condition gap is mitigated by the multi-laboratory sample set, tight E/uval margins across all three QoIs, and the conservative nature of the ASTM F1717 standard test configuration relative to in vivo loading. All remaining 12 factors meet or exceed required levels. The model is accepted for use in the COU as defined.",
